import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardTitle, CardText, Col, Form, Row } from 'reactstrap'

const Vehicle = () => {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardHeader className='border-bottom'>
          <CardTitle tag='h4'>Vehicles</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
        <CardBody>
        
      <Col lg='4' md='6' className='mb-1'>
      <Label className='form-label' for='Vehicle_No_Plate_Id'>
        Vehicle_No_Plate_Id:
      </Label>
      <Input id='Vehicle_No_Plate_Id' placeholder='Vehicle_No_Plate_Id' type="text"/>
    </Col>
    <Col lg='4' md='6' className='mb-1'>
      <Label className='form-label' for='Vehicle_Owner_Name'>
        Vehicle_Owner_Name:
      </Label>
      <Input
        type='text'
        id='Vehicle_Owner_Name'
        placeholder='Vehicle_Owner_Name'
      />
    </Col>
    <Col lg='4' md='6' className='mb-1'>
      <Label className='form-label' for='vehicle_type'>
        vehicle_type:
      </Label>
      <Input id='vehicle_type' placeholder='vehicle_type' type='text' />
    </Col>
    </CardBody>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Vehicle
